    <p>I was out sick from work today so ordering pizza is probably not a good idea.</p>
    <p>I’ve been thinking I should film myself eating in more interesting locations, or at least eating pizza from somewhere other than Pauline and Sharon’s. That makes my life so much more difficult though.</p>
